### --- MEDIA CRUD TESTS ---
# Replace the token value below with the token from the login response

@token = laurin-mrpToken
@mediaId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000


### Create new media entry
POST http://localhost:10001/api/media
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Inception",
  "description": "Dream within a dream.",
  "mediaType": "MOVIE",
  "releaseYear": 2010,
  "genres": ["Sci-Fi", "Thriller"],
  "ageRestriction": 12
}

### Get all media
GET http://localhost:10001/api/media
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get one media by ID
# Replace {{mediaId}} with actual ID from POST response
GET http://localhost:10001/api/media/{{mediaId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update existing media
PUT http://localhost:10001/api/media/{{mediaId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Inception (Extended)",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "mediaType": "MOVIE",
  "releaseYear": 2010,
  "genres": ["Sci-Fi", "Thriller"],
  "ageRestriction": 16
}

### Delete media
DELETE http://localhost:10001/api/media/{{mediaId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
